		<div class="col-md-12">
			<div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1_label" style='display:none'></div><div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1__ControlWrapper_OregonRichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" ><div class="well"><p class="lead">Stay informed, get involved, and navigate our Administrative Rules with ease.<br></p><p>This page serves as your central resource for accessing and understanding the Administrative Rules that guide Oregon Housing and Community Services. Whether you’re seeking specific details on OHCS’s Rules, looking to engage on any proposed rulemaking, or need information on the rulemaking process generally, you’ll find everything you need right here.&#160;</p><p></p><ul><li> 
         <span>If you would like any of this information in a language other than English, please email&#160;</span><a href="mailto&#58;Language.Access@hcs.oregon.gov">Language.Access@hcs.oregon.gov</a></li><li> 
         <span style="color&#58;#000000;font-size&#58;19.4688px;">To contact the OHCS Administrative Rules team, email&#160;</span><a href="mailto&#58;HCS_Rules_Team@hcs.oregon.gov" style="color&#58;#0e5f9b;padding&#58;0px 0.12rem;transition&#58;text-decoration-color 0.3s, color 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;font-size&#58;19.4688px;">HCS_Rules_Team@hcs.oregon.gov</a><span style="color&#58;#000000;font-size&#58;19.4688px;">, or call 503-986-6796.</span></li></ul><p></p> 
   <a class="ohcs-btn ohcs-btn-primary" href="https&#58;//secure.sos.state.or.us/oard/displayChapterRules.action?selectedChapter=144">OHCS Rules</a><a class="ohcs-btn ohcs-btn-primary" href="#comment-periods">Open comment periods</a><a class="ohcs-btn ohcs-btn-primary" href="#rule-filings">Rule filings</a><a class="ohcs-btn ohcs-btn-primary" href="/ohcs/get-involved/Pages/public-meeting-calendar.aspx">Rules calendar</a> </div><h2>Oregon's Housing Cost Impact</h2><p> 
   <span style="color&#58;#000000;font-size&#58;17.5px;">When OHCS&#160;engages in rulemaking, it includes on this page a statement of potential fiscal impact of the proposed rule; summary of the proposed rule; FAQ documents pertaining to the rulemaking; and minutes or recordings from rulemaking meetings. Public comments will also be published on this page during the rulema</span><span style="color&#58;#000000;font-size&#58;17.5px;">king process.</span></p><p>Find information about 
   <a href="/ohcs/get-involved/Pages/housing-cost-impact-statement.aspx">Oregon’s Housing Cost Impact Statement</a>.<br></p><h2>Engagement opportunities<br></h2><p>OHCS is always looking to bring interested people into our rulemaking process. If you would like to participate in a future rulemaking engagement, please&#160;reach out using the 
   <a href="#rules-form">Rules Engagement Form.</a><br></p><h3>Upcoming rules advisory committee</h3>
Oregon Rehousing Initiative (ORI)<br><div><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;">More information coming soon<br style="color&#58;#000000;"><span style="color&#58;#000000;">RAC Date&#58; 01/13/2026</span></span></font></div><div><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;"><br></span></font></div><div><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;"><span style="color&#58;#000000;"></span></span></font><span style="color&#58;#000000;">Oregon Affordable Housing Tax Credit (OAHTC)</span><br style="color&#58;#000000;"><div style="color&#58;#000000;"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;">More information coming soon</span></div><div style="color&#58;#000000;"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;">RAC Date&#58; 01/20/2026</span></font></div><div style="color&#58;#000000;"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color&#58;#000000;">Publicly <span style="font-size&#58;17.9688px;">Supported Housing Contract Preservation (PuSH)</span><br style="color&#58;#000000;"><div style="color&#58;#000000;"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;">More information coming soon<br>RAC Date&#58; 01/29/2026</span></font></div><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;"></span></font></div><div><h3 id="comment-periods">Open public comment periods&#58; January 1 through January 31, 2026<br></h3><p>When OHCS&#160;opens&#160;the public comment periods on proposed administrative rule changes for any rules within Chapter 813, rules public hearing information will be listed&#160;below.&#160;<br></p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;">General Housing Account</span></font><br style="color&#58;#000000;font-size&#58;19.4688px;"><div style="color&#58;#000000;font-size&#58;19.4688px;"><font color="#000000"><a href="https&#58;//ormswd2.synergydcs.com/HPRMWebDrawer3/Record/721274" style="text-decoration&#58;underline;">Rulemaking Engagement Record</a><br>Public Hearing Date&#58; 01/20/2026</font></div><div style="color&#58;#000000;font-size&#58;19.4688px;"><font color="#000000">Public Hearing Time&#58; 11 - 11&#58;30 a.m.</font></div><div style="color&#58;#000000;font-size&#58;19.4688px;text-decoration&#58;underline;"><font color="#000000"><a href="https&#58;//events.gcc.teams.microsoft.com/event/bb6b10fe-09be-4d46-8139-95f377745b72%40aa3f6932-fa7c-47b4-a0ce-a598cad161cf">TEAM Webinar Link - Registration is Required - GHAP</a></font></div><p style="color&#58;#000000;">
      <span style="font-size&#58;19.4688px;"> 
         <a href="/transparency/Pages/administrative-rules.aspx">Oregon Transparency Administrative Rules</a>&#160;(web&#160;link)</span></p></div></div></div>
