   <a href="mailto&#58;HCS_DL_HCS_Rules_Team@hcs.oregon.gov">HCS_DL_HCS_Rules_Team@hcs.oregon.gov</a>. Please include the rule referenced in the subject line of the email.</p><hr /><h2 id="rule-filings">Rule filings</h2><div class="ms-rtestate-read ms-rte-wpbox"><div class="ms-rtestate-notify  ms-rtestate-read cb0b6ea8-fcc1-43fb-a6c2-ebafe6ab5aaf" id="div_cb0b6ea8-fcc1-43fb-a6c2-ebafe6ab5aaf" unselectable="on"><div id="MSOZoneCell_WebPartWPQ1" class="s4-wpcell-plain ms-webpartzone-cell ms-webpart-cell-vertical ms-fullWidth ">
